# Hugging Face Hub / Spaces: exclude paths from uploads where tooling respects this file.
# Official `upload_folder()` primarily honors root `.gitignore`; this file documents
# Hub-oriented exclusions and mirrors `.dockerignore` so Docker builds and Hub syncs stay aligned.
#
# If your client only reads `.gitignore`, rely on the expanded `.gitignore` in this repo;
# Docker always reads `.dockerignore` for `COPY .` during Space builds.

.git
.github

__pycache__
**/__pycache__
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache
.venv
venv
